<subSubSection id="91E06561FFC20D25FF7AF549FCE3F4F9" pageId="5" pageNumber="460" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="D94536EAFFC20D25FF7AF549FCE3F4F9" blockId="5.[171,1379,2348,2931]" pageId="5" pageNumber="460">
<emphasis id="EB8EEAF8FFC20D25FF7AF549FDB9F50A" bold="true" box="[173,526,2741,2774]" pageId="5" pageNumber="460">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Kalinowski's 
<taxonomicName id="1EFA4D69FFC20D25FF27F521FEF9F522" box="[240,334,2781,2814]" class="Mammalia" family="Cuniculidae" genus="Agouti" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="5" pageNumber="460" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Agouti</taxonomicName>
might be threatened, but there is very little information on its extent of occurrence,status, and ecological requirements.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
